<li>1808. Newneham and others on the state of Ireland. <i>Edinburgh Review</i> <b>12</b>, July, 336-355.</li>
<li>1809. Newneham on the state of Ireland, <i>Edinburgh Review</i> <b>14</b> April, 151-170.</li>
<li>1811. Depreciation of paper currency. <i>Edinburgh Review</i> <b>17</b>, February, 340-372.</li>
<li>1812. Pamphlets on the bullion question. <i>Edinburgh Review</i> <b>18</b>, August, 448-470.</li>
