<p><a name="Footnotes" id="Footnotes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Thomas_Malthus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=30" title="Edit section: Footnotes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Footnotes</span></h2>
