ki/Johann_Heinrich_von_Th%C3%BCnen" title="Johann Heinrich von Thünen">Johann Heinrich von Thünen</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/John_Stuart_Mill" title="John Stuart Mill">John Stuart Mill</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Henry_Charles_Carey" title="Henry Charles Carey">Henry Charles Carey</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Nassau_William_Senior" title="Nassau William Senior">Nassau William Senior</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Edward_Gibbon_Wakefield" title="Edward Gibbon Wakefield">Edward Gibbon Wakefield</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/John_Rae_(economist)" title="John Rae (economist)">John Rae</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Fr%C3%A9d%C3%A9ric_Bastiat" title="Frédéric Bastiat">Frédéric Bastiat</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Thomas_Tooke" title="Thomas Tooke">Thomas Tooke</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Robert_Torrens_(economist)" title="Robert Torrens (economist)">Robert Torrens</a></span></p>
